eAddress)))\\\\\\\\n    }\\\\\\\\n  }\\\\\\\\n}\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"exit_code\\\\\\\":0,\\\\\\\"status\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"completed\\\\\\\"}}\\\\n33:{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"item.completed\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"item\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"item_17\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"command_execution\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"command\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"/usr/bin/bash -lc \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"git diff --stat 5e4ba8828ca690826006f806c5c700a4b2ef4cca 319a247eb28c3ebcf20ab962de86c986ca20eb20 && echo '---' && git diff --name-status 5e4ba8828ca690826006f806c5c700a4b2ef4cca 319a247eb28c3ebcf20ab962de86c986ca20eb20\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"aggregated_output\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\" .../1.3.0/reachability-metadata.json               | 755 +++++++++++++++++++++\\\\\\\\n .../pekko-http-core_3/1.3.0/build.gradle           |   1 +\\\\\\\\n .../pekko_http_core_3/Http2AlpnSupportTest.scala   |  79 +++\\\\\\\\n .../pekko_http_core_3/Pekko_http_core_3Test.scala  |  16 -\\\\\\\\n 4 files changed, 835 insertions(+), 16 deletions(-)\\\\\\\\n---\\\\\\\\nA\\\\\\\\tmetadata/org.apache.pekko/pekko-http-core_3/1.3.0/reachability-metadata.json\\\\\\\\nM\\\\\\\\ttests/src/org.apache.pekko/pekko-http-core_3/1.3.0/build.gradle\\\\\\\\nA\\\\\\\\ttests/src/org.apache.pekko/pekko-http-core_3/1.3.0/src/test/scala/org_apache_pekko/pekko_http_core_3/Http2AlpnSupportTest.scala\\\\\\\\nD\\\\\\\\ttests/src/org.apache.pekko/pekko-http-core_3/1.3.0/src/test/scala/org_apache_pekko/pekko_http_core_3/Pekko_http_core_3Test.scala\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"exit_code\\\\\\\":0,\\\\\\\"status\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"completed\\\\\\\"}}\\\\n34:{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"item.started\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"item\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"item_18\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"command_execution\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"command\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"/usr/bin/bash -lc 'for f in forge/logs/org.apache.pekko:pekko-http-core_3:1.3.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-10T23-15-10-020966Z.log forge/logs/org.apache.pekko:pekko-http-core_3:1.3.0/g